'''詹姆士·葛雷'''（{{lang-en|James Gray}}，{{bd|1969年|4月14日}}）是一位美國男導演、製片人和編劇。

== 生平 ==
葛雷出生於美國[[紐約市|紐約市]]的[[猶太人|猶太人]]家庭<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cannes-james-gray-immigrant-marion-526204|title=Cannes: James Gray on 'The Immigrant,' Marion Cotillard and Returning to the Fest (Q&A)|author=|last=Kilday|first=Gregg|date=May 21, 2013|work=The Hollywood Reporter|accessdate=June 11, 2018|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129120210/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cannes-james-gray-immigrant-marion-526204|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-lost-city-gray-20161017-snap-story.html|title=Director James Gray goes on his own search while creating 'The Lost City of Z'|accessdate=June 11, 2018|date=October 17, 2016|last=Zeitchik|first=Steven|work=Los Angeles Times|quote=And he is. He's also a grade-A kibitzer, a gregarious character, whose chatty and self-effacing wit bespeaks his Queens upbringing and Eastern European-Jewish heritage.|archive-date=2020-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200717035625/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-lost-city-gray-20161017-snap-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2017/04/of-immigrants-and-the-city-a-james-gray-retrospect.html|title=Of Immigrants and the City: A James Gray Retrospective|accessdate=June 11, 2018|author=|date=April 20, 2017|last=Jeng|first=Jonah|work=Paste Magazine|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2019-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190727215840/https://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2017/04/of-immigrants-and-the-city-a-james-gray-retrospect.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="indiewire">{{cite web|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/james-gray-nicolas-winding-refn-more-giving-masterclasses-at-2013-marrakech-international-film-festival-20131105|title=James Gray, Nicolas Winding Refn & More Giving Masterclasses At 2013 Marrakech International Film Festival|work=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]|first=Kevin|last=Jagernauth|date=2013-11-05|access-date=2016-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140305051858/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/james-gray-nicolas-winding-refn-more-giving-masterclasses-at-2013-marrakech-international-film-festival-20131105|archive-date=2014-03-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，在紐約的[[皇后區|皇后區]]靠近Flushing Meadow的地區長大。他是[[俄羅斯猶太人|俄羅斯猶太人]]後裔<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thejc.com/culture/film/james-gray-film-1.435056|title=James Gray: Exploring the dark and personal|accessdate=June 11, 2018|date=March 27, 2017|last=Applebaum|first=Stephen|work=The Jewish Chronicle|archive-date=2021-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422233758/https://www.thejc.com/culture/film/james-gray-film-1.435056|dead-url=no}}</ref>，祖父母來自[[舊奧斯特羅皮利|舊奧斯特羅皮利]]。葛雷於[[南加州大学电影艺术学院|南加州大学电影艺术学院]]就讀時，他的學生作品《牛仔與天使》獲得製片人{{le|保羅·韋伯斯特|Paul Webster}}的注意，被鼓勵寫一篇劇本讓他監製，繼而誕生處女作《[[殺手怨曲|殺手怨曲]]》。

1994年，年僅25歲的葛雷以作品《殺手怨曲》贏得1994[[威尼斯电影节|威尼斯影展]]的[[銀獅獎_(電影)|銀獅獎]]。

其後的作品有五部入選為[[坎城影展|坎城影展]]正式競賽。

==個人生活==
葛雷在2005年與紀錄片製作人Alexandra Dickson結婚。二人有三個孩子<ref>{{cite web|author1=Gregg Kilday|title=Cannes: James Gray on 'The Immigrant,' Marion Cotillard and Returning to the Fest (Q&A)|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cannes-james-gray-immigrant-marion-526204|publisher=The Hollywood Reporter|accessdate=2018-04-19|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129120210/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cannes-james-gray-immigrant-marion-526204|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

